				<wikidot:authorName>Faraday Cage</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856658</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Cosntructive criticism:</p> <p><em>The second Clockwork turns towards the civilian and nods. &quot;You should have been useful first.&quot;</em></p> <p>I had problems determining out if the civilian being referred to above was some random onlooker or the civilian being shaken about or any other random civilian.</p> <p>Edit : I eventually figured it out but it took two entire rereads to understand. I'm not sure anymore if the problem is my own stupidity or murky writing.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
